snippet.title: Astrea: Six-Sided Oracles - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Buddy breaks down the ins and outs, ups and downs of Astrea's second playable Oracle, Cellarius! A berserker feeding on the damage he takes on, Cellarius' specialty is pumping up for huge hits of gigantic damage!
